HEADWORD: Ovisac
<hw>O"vi*sac</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Ov</ets>um +
<ets>sac</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A Graafian
follicle; any sac containing an ovum or ova.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The
inner layer of the fibrous wall of a Graafian follicle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

